{"tid":643539,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]  傳歐柏嘉擬保留俄鋁控制權　期鋁飆升","createTime":"2018-04-26T14:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T14:59:14.000Z","uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cf462feaf90634ed83d553d532e9e83ec7a20539","tid":643539,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"外媒消息指，俄鋁(00486)大股東歐柏嘉(Oleg Deripaska)計劃保留俄鋁的控制權。消息傳出後，鋁價短線快速飆升。倫敦金屬交易所(LME)三個月期鋁短線抽上逾3%，高見每噸2,316美元。<br />\n<br />\n美國早前對俄鋁進行制裁，其後態度軟化，但有傳條件是要歐柏嘉放棄對俄鋁的控制權，才考慮不對其進行制裁。「放生」消息一度刺激俄鋁股價大反撲，周四收市價為2.1港元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://money18.on.cc/finnews/news_breaking_content.html?section=exp&amp;article_id=bkn-20180426213102243-0426_00842_001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmoney18.on.cc%2Ffinnews%2Fnews_breaking_content.html%3Fsection%3Dexp%26article_id%3Dbkn-20180426213102243-0426_00842_001&d=7rqFycSoXiR%2BlvFX%2B%2FLSDKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=3d440ecb\" target=\"_blank\">http://money18.on.cc/finnews/news_breaking_content.html?section=exp&amp;article_id=bkn-20180426213102243-0426_00842_001</a>"},{"pid":"2c2e89e0a03fbeb7f7bc48e1d4b5db601ab0bb5f","tid":643539,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T14:59:14.000Z","msg":"跌返去 1.6 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}